    "Therefore, in addition to the abovementioned contributions, our research contributes to the explanation capability, quality, and users' perception of or explanation in an explainable recommender system (Lipton, 1990).",
    "Our study has multiple implications from practitioners' perspectives.",
    "Firstly, our study detects that designers and developers must exploit the affordance or duality of explainable recommendation systems to develop an explainable social media recommendation.",
